From cbbrowne at gmail.com  Sun Nov  2 03:20:56 2014
From: cbbrowne at gmail.com (Christopher Browne)
Date: Sat, 1 Nov 2014 23:20:56 -0400
Subject: [GTALUG] teksavvy dsl 2 modem that runs OpenWRT
