Sorry for the somewhat off topic nature of this note.

My wife's employer, a computer services company in Aurora, ON is looking
for a technician to help support their clients. They need someone with PC
break/fix experience. Their OS needs are primarily Windows -- in particular
Active Directory knowledge and MS Exchange. They would probably look on
Linux experience as a bonus, but Linux is not the main job focus.

If there is any interest in this opportunity, drop me a note directly (not
through the list) and I will provide the contact information where you can
send your resume. Don't send me any resumes or personal information, as I
have no direct connection to the company or the recruitment effort, but am
just facilitating my wife's wish to make this opportunity known to the
widest possible technical audience.

Thanks,

Do-Ming Lum
