Subject: [GTALUG] Crypto Question: Where do you get your entropy
In-Reply-To: <CAAsTreDL5=H=S0SSedyHJR_9mwFNzmJTyTed_zscwsUmV9sS9Q@mail.gmail.com>
References: <alpine.LRH.2.02.1411120055080.6002@redclaw.mimosa.com>
 <CAFNqd5U_L=tWdgd7hWrszEsb5zjTK67wwO-wTnF+F5QARw8Wew@mail.gmail.com>
