From sgh at vex.net  Thu Nov 13 21:14:06 2014
From: sgh at vex.net (Steve Harvey)
Date: Thu, 13 Nov 2014 16:14:06 -0500
Subject: [GTALUG] Thinkpad choices today?
In-Reply-To: <301BD39D-8FC1-4AEA-A002-8AF0339BF910@ss.org>
