I was going to second the C720 comment, but I'm reduced to third
because Daniel beat me to it.  I have the same Chromebook he does (I
think mine has a bigger SSD than his, but they're otherwise
identical), and its been lovely.

My experience with the Atoms has been that my 2010 Atom-based netbook
makes my 2005 Pentium-M laptop look like an absolute speed demon.  I
really, really don't like the Atom.

