The price of the 27" U2713 is now $349 (vs $834 regular $729 sale price on
dell.ca (was $259 when I purchased), and the 30" U3014 at Walmart.ca is
$349 vs Dell's normal price of $1599 discounted now to $1199. The Walmart
page lists a Dell model number that varies slightly in the letters at the
end compared to the Dell site. Buying now, I'd go for the 30".

