I will at least get one, but now price is getting closer to their 4k dells,
so have to think about it, now of course
their 4k price may be out of sync, but it is closer to the best price i
have seen else where. 350$ is still less then
1/2 the typical low price, but given as you say how screwy their prices
are, I have little confidence the 350$ is going
to stick. Worst part is, if 350$ isn't going to stick, they will still be
shipping all these out to customers incorrectly.
Maybe with a little luck Dell screwed up its bulk custom pricing to WalMart
and walmart will be able to honour and Dell will eat it. (ok i can dream).

