From avolkov at gmail.com  Fri Nov 21 18:09:17 2014
From: avolkov at gmail.com (Alex Volkov)
Date: Fri, 21 Nov 2014 13:09:17 -0500
Subject: [GTALUG] teksavvy dsl 2 modem that runs OpenWRT
In-Reply-To: <CAArSzsUcSwzgxMe2mismFYHMWrXzhYcj7NH8LSPg+9SfkgoRow@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CAO1j=qf+gvG6ap8RiZLNOu78-BZ0mEo8Nhyy8yS=jSmymx7tXA@mail.gmail.com>
