On 20/11/2014 7:02 AM, Scott Allen wrote:
> They also corrected the model number in the Specifications section
> from U2713HM to S2440LCA. Everything else appears to be unchanged.
>
> Note that the UPC code specified has always been the correct one for
> the 24" S2440L. I bet this is what counts since that's probably what
